window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Heads you win. Tails I lose.</b>&nbsp;</p> <p>Everything is falling apart.&nbsp;</p> <p>Magnus is hunting Eris, and even the gods fear him. As if that weren’t enough, our criminal dealings have finally caught up with us. The Merchants Guild are coming to settle all accounts, and we’re deep in the red.</p> <p>Enemies from every corner of the world are closing in, and the fate of Nexus balances on the edge of the wars we will fight.&nbsp;</p> <p>I have a choice to make and whatever I choose, I can only lose.</p>"; 
